"Malko J.","CCS technologies in the european energy markets [Technologie CCS na europejskim rynku energii]",2011,"Rynek Energii","97","6",,"3","11",,,,"http://www.scopus.com/inward/record.url?eid=2-s2.0-84863887719&partnerID=40&md5=041f22a04390eec82d8a2e1d3663c7dd",,"Malko, J.","The use of carbon capture and storage ( CCS ) on an industrial and commercial scale is essential to any hope of meeting global climate change targets. While the components pieces of the technology exist, the application of the technique and assessment of the economical effectiveness are in its infancy. Full-scale deployment has yet to be achieved on fossil fuel power plant anywhere. In the presented paper Carbon Capture and Storage technologies in the European competitive energy markets on the basis of the numerical model LIBEMOD, used to identify the 2030 market equilibrium, are discussed. Review of various sources for CCS technical efficiency and cost estimates, for the existing coal and gas power plants, retrofitted by CCS and new (greenfields) ones are performed. Some discussions and conclusions are also presented.","CCS cost; Energy market; Energy technologies; European Union",,,,,,,"Aune, F.N., (2008) Liberalizing European Energy Markets - An Economic Analysis, , Edward Elgar, Cheltenham (UK) and Northampton (US); (2010) Roadmap 2050 - A Practical Guide to A Prosperous Low Carbon Economy, , European Climate Foundation ECF Apr; Golombek, R., Carbon capture and storage technologies in the European power market (2011) The Energy Journal IAEE, 32 (3); (2009) World Energy Outlook 2008, , International Energy Agency OECD/IEA, Paris; Europejska, K., Komunikat do Parlamentu Europejskiego (⋯) Europejska polityka energetyczna (2007) KOM, 1. , wersja ostateczna Bruksela, styczeń 2007; Europejska, K., Komunikat do Parlamentu Europejskiego (⋯) Plan działania prowadza̧cy do przejścia na konkurencyjna̧ gospodarkȩ niskoemisyjna̧ do 2050 r (2011) KOM, p. 112. , wersja ostateczna, Bruksela marzec 201; Metz, B., (2005) IPCC Special Report on Carbon Dioxide Capture and Storage, , Cambr. Univ.- N.York; (2009) Polityka Energetyczna Polski Do 2030 Roku, , Ministerstwo Gospodarki Dokument przyjȩty przez Radȩ Ministrów, Warszawa","Malko, J.",,,,,,,,14255960,,,,"Polish","Rynek Energ.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-84863887719
